      <p class="text-sm mb-5" style="color:#326177;line-height:1.7;">Phone signal dies inside festivals. Totems are how groups find each other in the crowd. Check back here before each event — we'll post where groups will be gathering and what totems to look for.</p>

      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="tip-card" style="border:2px dashed rgba(168,85,247,0.3);background:rgba(168,85,247,0.02);">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined flex-shrink-0" style="color:#a855f7;font-size:28px;font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">flag</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-base mb-1" style="color:#003345;">Totem info coming soon</p>
              <p class="text-sm" style="color:#326177;line-height:1.6;">We'll post meetup locations and totem descriptions for each festival before the event. Follow us and check back here closer to April. In the meantime — join the <a href="/meetup" style="color:#a855f7;font-weight:700;">Who's Going</a> page to find others attending the same events.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip-card good">
