            <span class="material-symbols-outlined flex-shrink-0" style="color:#34C759;font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">tips_and_updates</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color:#003345;">What's a totem?</p>
              <p class="text-sm" style="color:#326177;line-height:1.6;">A totem is a tall, visible object someone carries at a festival so their group can find them in a crowd. Usually something on a pole — a flag, a funny sign, a decorated umbrella. When signal fails and WhatsApp goes dark, you find the totem.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── BUY/SELL TICKETS ── -->
