      <p class="text-sm mb-5" style="color:#326177;line-height:1.7;">Plans changed? Festival sold out? Our peer-to-peer ticket marketplace lets you buy and sell tickets for any Songkran event safely within the community.</p>

      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="tip-card purple">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" style="color:#a855f7;font-size:22px;font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">confirmation_number</span>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color:#003345;">How it works</p>
              <ul class="text-sm space-y-1.5" style="color:#326177;">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined flex-shrink-0" style="font-size:14px;color:#a855f7;margin-top:1px;">sell</span>Post a listing — festival, tier, price, your contact handle (Telegram, WhatsApp, Instagram)</li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined flex-shrink-0" style="font-size:14px;color:#a855f7;margin-top:1px;">search</span>Browse listings — unlock contact info with your email (one-time, no account needed)</li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="material-symbols-outlined flex-shrink-0" style="font-size:14px;color:#a855f7;margin-top:1px;">handshake</span>Deal directly — agree on payment and transfer outside the platform</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tip-card warn">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined flex-shrink-0" style="color:#FF9F0A;font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">warning</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color:#003345;">Always verify before paying</p>
              <p class="text-sm" style="color:#326177;">Meet in a public place to exchange tickets where possible. Ask for proof of purchase. Never pay full price upfront to someone you can't verify. Use PayPal Goods & Services or bank transfer with the seller's name confirmed.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/tickets" class="btn btn-primary" style="display:inline-flex;">
