              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-1 text-xs" style="color:#326177;">
                <span><strong style="color:#003345;">GCircuit (Emsphere):</strong> BTS Phrom Phong · 3 min walk</span>
                <span><strong style="color:#003345;">Silom / GOD / Soi 2&4:</strong> BTS Sala Daeng</span>
                <span><strong style="color:#003345;">Sukhumvit bars:</strong> BTS Nana or Asok</span>
                <span><strong style="color:#003345;">Siam Songkran (RCA):</strong> BTS Phetchaburi + short taxi</span>
              </div>
            </div>
