            <span class="material-symbols-outlined flex-shrink-0" style="color:#ef4444;font-size:20px;font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">car_crash</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color:#003345;">Grab will fail you after big events — have cash ready</p>
              <p class="text-sm" style="color:#326177;line-height:1.6;">After any festival ends (GCircuit, S2O, Siam Songkran) thousands of people open Grab at the same time. The app either finds no drivers or surges 4–5×. Have <strong style="color:#003345;">฿500–800 cash</strong> for local tuk-tuks or metered taxis. Negotiate the price before you get in — local drivers know the situation and will charge more, but it's still faster than waiting.</p>
