              <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color:#003345;">Ride app tips</p>
              <p class="text-sm" style="color:#326177;line-height:1.6;">Download <strong style="color:#003345;">Bolt</strong> (often cheaper than Grab during surge) and <strong style="color:#003345;">InDriver</strong> (you name your price). Walk 10–15 minutes from the venue exit before opening any app — prices drop significantly away from the crowd.</p>
