              <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color:#003345;">Waterproof everything at pool parties</p>
              <p class="text-sm" style="color:#326177;">Buy a waterproof phone pouch at any 7-Eleven (฿80–100). Leave your wallet at the hotel — just bring one card and cash in a zip-lock bag.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip-card warn">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined flex-shrink-0" style="color:#FF9F0A;font-size:20px;font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">thermostat</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1" style="color:#003345;">Heat exhaustion is very real</p>
              <p class="text-sm" style="color:#326177;">38–42°C, dancing, drinking, direct sun. Drink a bottle of water every hour. Coconut water from street stalls has electrolytes. Dizzy or nauseated = find shade and drink water immediately.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tip-card info">
